					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"d7d2c606-823e-4839-b009-a3401e1f5dc8\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"living-soulcasting\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Living Soulcasting</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"2c464b00-deb6-49ae-9100-f2bdb3f4230b\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Two Actions\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Two Actions\">2</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"55322368-f1ff-4242-a649-cf37ba122551\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You’ve practiced techniques for Soulcasting blood, allowing you to cleanse the body of poison and to speed recovery from injuries.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"91340dfb-1904-441b-a426-1e088b30c5ea\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">While touching a character, spend 1 <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"investiture\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Investiture</tooltip> and make a DC 15 Transformation test to cleanse their blood. On a success, the effects of any poison end for the target, and you can reduce the recovery time of one of their <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"injuries\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">injuries</tooltip> by 5 days.</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"80dfff9b-e05d-41ac-aaa2-6e75efd798a7\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">The GM can spend <span aria-label=\"Complication\" class=\"icon-font-red icon\" title=\"Complication\">C</span> from this test to reduce the target’s maximum health by twice their level until after the target’s next long rest.</p>",
