							"value": "<p chunk_id=\"6155b5cc-0cc4-4d6f-8483-b08963c6a623\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat ParaOverride-2\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"flamecasting\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Flamecasting</tooltip> talent</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"403fc301-278b-4840-a4af-febfd7d75b58\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Activation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"e574f286-0dde-40da-bcee-447ae1ee971c\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You’ve become so powerful that you can Soulcast larger objects with much greater efficiency.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"6400f983-f861-4c15-aab7-32629061a155\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">When you Soulcast non-living material, reduce the <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"investiture\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Investiture</tooltip> cost by 2 (to a minimum of 1 Investiture). For example, it now costs you only 1 Investiture to Soulcast either a Small, Medium, or Large object.</p>",
