					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"99a64e84-a57e-4efe-b689-51bd25d8c829\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> Speak the First Ideal</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"1e32838b-e996-4eca-845e-e71ef1618bdb\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Two Actions\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Two Actions\">2</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"49f84e14-bf33-4e30-809a-52e1eb35940e\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You’ve mastered the subtleties of affecting living flesh with Soulcasting.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"c7c08b77-65d5-4439-a39c-c7f9930f21e3\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">Spend 1 <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"investiture\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Investiture</tooltip> and make a melee Transformation attack against the Spiritual defense of a character, plant, or other living organism within your reach. Roll 3d4 spirit damage. The size of these damage dice increases with your ranks in Transformation; at 2 ranks, roll 3d6 (instead of 3d4), and so on.</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"0aaf1584-e786-4d7a-a8bd-43c911196109\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">If this reduces the target to 0 health, they die, and you transform their body into your choice of material without spending additional actions or Investiture.</p>",
